project_descr: Support Government of Iraq (GoI) in establishing the enabling, predictable, easy business environment for the Private Sector development of Iraq, through endorsement of the Private Sector Development Strategy of Iraq

Increased sub-national capacity for facilitating private sector role in local economic development and job generation
